##   rel1: upgraded to v3.0c, kernel24 2.4.30, kernel24-grsec 2.4.30-grsec, kernel26 2.6.11.7 2005.04.13
##   rel5: upgraded to kernel26 2.6.11 2005.03.03
##   rel4: gzip modules 2005.02.26
